propChildren: The content of the table, normally `TableHead` and `TableBody`.
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propComponent:
The component used for the root node.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propPadding: Allows TableCells to inherit padding of the Table.
propSize: Allows TableCells to inherit size of the Table.
propStickyHeader:
Set the header sticky.

⚠️ It doesn't work with IE11.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesStickyHeader: Styles applied to the root element if `stickyHeader={true}`.
